      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nu peedohd man/ lub\nDsams/ mannus Grehkus/ un\ngreesees ar mannim atpakat/ ka\neß to KUNGU peefauzu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazztja Samuels us\nSaulu: Es ne atgreesifchohs ar\ntew/ tapehz ka tu ta KUNGA\nWahrdv eßi atmettis/ tad irr tas\nKUNGS tew atkat atmettis/\nka tew ne buhs par Kehniau buht\npahr Israëlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad nu Samuels greesehs\nno-eet/ tad fatwehre tas winna\nSwahrku Stuhri/ un ta plihfe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazztja Samuels us\nto: Tas KUNGS irr schodeen\nto Israëta Walstibu no tewim\nnoplehßis/ un tawain Tuwakain\ndewis/ kas labbaks irr ne ka tu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas/ kas Israëta Stip-\nruuns irr/ ne mello/ un tam ne kas\nschehl nahkahs/ jo wiꞥſch ne irr\nweens Zilweks/ ka winnam kas\nschehl buhtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wisch tad fazztja : Es\neftmu grehtojs/ Nu tad/ gehdi\nman jelle preekfch teem Wezza-\njeem mannu Saulchu un Israëta\nPreekfchâ/ un atgreesees ar man-\nni/ ka es to KUNGii tawu Dee-\nwu peeluhsu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atgreesehs Samuels\nSaulam pakat/ un Sauls pee-\nluhdse to KUNGu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazztja Samuels:\nWeddeet man schurp Agagu to\nAmalekiteeu Kehniau/ un Agags\ngahje pee winnu wehligi/ un A-\ngags fazztja : Teefcham tahc\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nahwes Ruhktuuns irr (n-\nmannim) nohst.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazztja Samuels\nItt ka taws Schbins tahm Se-\nwahm favus Behrmus laupijs\nta taps tawai Mahteifawi Beh-\nnt laupiti starp tahm Seewahm\nTa fakappaja Samuels to Aga-\ngu preekfsch ta KUNGA eekfa\nGilgala.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz gahje Samuels uh\nRabinatu/ un Sauls gahje fa-\nwâ Namma uhs Gibeju Saula\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Samuels wairs u-\nredseja to Saulu/ lihds winna\nMirfchanaß Deenai/tatschu Sa-\nmuels bija noskumnis Saul-\ndeht/ un ka tam KUNGA\nbija schehl/ ka winsch Saulu pa-\nKehniau darrijs pahr Israëlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XVI. Nodalla.\nDeews fuhta Samuelu uhs Betlemi pee Ifa-\njn/ weenu no winna Dehleem par Kehnia-\nswaidiht : 1/4. Schis Gohds tohp tam ma-\nsakam/ Dahwidam parahvihts : 11. Ween-\ntaus Gars nahk pahr Saulu : 14. Da-\nwids tohp Saula Pilli xemts : 19. Ka ta-\nta Kehniau Bruuku Nessejs un Spehlmari-\nnis effus : 21/32.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad fazztja tas KUNG-\nus Samuels : Zik ilg-\ntu schehlojees pahr Sau-\nlu/ kur es tomehr winnu efmi-\natmettis/ ka tam ne buhs pa-\nKehniau buht pahr Israëlu/ pi-\ndi tawu Raggu ar Efji/ un ei-\nprohjam/ es fuhtifchu tew pee If-\nsaju to Betlemiteri/ jo es efmi-\nno winna Dehleem wan ween-\nKehniau isredsejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Samuels fazztja: Ra-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
